<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Overview</h3>
    <p class="text-block_role">Role: UX, Web Design</p>
    <p class="text-block_copy">The brand team at Hook and Loop set out with a very lofty goal to complete a website redesign and rebranding in under 2 months time. They wanted to reveal the new site at Inforum, our annual customer conference. In order to complete this in time, the project was divided by page and split among the product designers. The team was made up of five designers, one Information Architect and one Art Director.</p>
</section>

