<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Challenge</h3>
    <p class="text-block_copy">Time was obviously the biggest challenge we faced with this project. We had to streamline processes that might take weeks into a single day. The designers created options in the morning and we reviewed in the afternoon. It was very fast-paced design decisions. I was chosen to focus on the homepage redesign which was dependent on the final designs of the other pages (blog, case studies, etc.).</p>
</section>

