<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Solution</h3>
    <p class="text-block_copy">We learned a lot in the short time we spent working together. Most importantly, we learned what didn't work. Although the team came together to streamline our work process and deliver a complete redesign in under a month, the time left for development wasn't enough and we missed our launch goal. We also realized that dividing out the pages, while in theory seemed like a quicker way to work, ultimately took longer because we weren't looking at the site as a whole.</p>
</section>
